\b\fs28 System Requirements\

\b0\fs24 \
This version of otterlace will only work on Mac OS X version 10.6 and later, and only on Intel CPU machines.\
\

\b\fs28 Installation
\b0\fs24 \
\
To install the otterlace client, drag the "otterlace" application from the installation disk to the Applications folder (or any other folder) on your Mac's hard disk.\
\
If you do not have a preferences file, otterlace will set one up for you when you first run it.\
\

